==English==
===Etymology===
From Latin ''[[irrumpere]]''

===Verb===
'''irrupt'''
#''(transitive)'' Break into.
#''(intransitive)'' Enter [[forcibly]] or uninvited.
#''(intransitive)'' [[Increase]] rapidly.
#''(intransitive)'' [[Intensify]] suddenly.
#''Misspelling of'' [[erupt]].

